div.h2: IP Anonymization: SHA-256 Hash with Per-Service Salt

text.tspan: // hashIP returns SHA-256(ip + salt) as 64-char hex string.
// hashIP returns SHA-256(ip + salt) as 64-char hex string.

div.p: DANGER ZONE Raw IP GDPR-sensitive Never written to DB Never logged
salt purpose: Prevents rainbow table attack. Attacker with DB access cannot reverse ip_hash raw IP without knowing this secret value.
[]byte(ip + salt) Go string concat before byte conversion. No separator needed salt length is fixed.
Analytics DB schema: ip_hash TEXT NOT NULL -- ip_raw: never stored
